OL,3,CArsonist admits setting fire to Tory
OL,4,CMP Mike Freer's shed in north London
OL,6,FA man has admitted setting fire to a
OL,7,Fshed belonging to Conservative MP Mike
OL,8,FFreer ` but denied it was politically
OL,9,Fmotivated.
OL,11,FPaul Harwood, 42, was charged over a
OL,12,Ffire last Christmas Eve at the MP's
OL,13,Fconstituency office in Ballards Lane,
OL,14,Fnorth Finchley, north London.
OL,16,FThe defendant, who lives in Ballards
OL,17,FLane, was also charged over another
OL,18,Farson attack on a bin at the rear of a
OL,19,Fproperty in Long Lane, Finchley, on
OL,20,Fthe same night.
