OL,3,CArsonist admits setting fire to Tory
OL,4,CMP Mike Freer's shed in north London
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, he appeared at the Old
OL,7,FBailey via video link and pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to two charges of arson.
OL,10,FThe charge relating to the MP stated
OL,11,Fthat on December 24 2023 he "damaged
OL,12,Fby fire to a shed...belonging to Mike
OL,13,FFreer intending to damage such
OL,14,Fproperty or being reckless as to
OL,15,Fwhether such property would be damaged
OL,16,Fand being reckless as to whether life
OL,17,Fto others would be endangered".
