OL,6,FJudge John Lodge set a further hearing
OL,7,Ffor March 12 and remanded the
OL,8,Fdefendants into custody.
OL,10,FMr Freer, 63, was appointed
OL,11,FParliamentary Under Secretary of State
OL,12,Ffor the Ministry of Justice on 20
OL,13,FSeptember 2022.
OL,15,FHe served as minister for exports and
OL,16,Fminister for equalities between
OL,17,FSeptember 2021 and 6 July 2022.
OL,19,FHe was first elected as MP for
OL,20,FFinchley and Golders Green in May 2010.
